text.en_US: The entrance seems to be blocked from the outside.
text.pt_BR: A entrada parece estar bloqueada do lado de fora.
text.de_DE: Der Eingang scheint von außen blockiert.
text.zh_CN: 入口似乎被从外面挡住了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/09/11]
text.ja_JP: 外から塞がっているようです。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/09/11]
text.zh_TW: 入口似乎被從外面擋住了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/09/11]

message.ja_JP: ダンジョンレーーース！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: You don't have to wish me luck. Just run slow and I'll be happy.
message.pt_BR: Não precisa me desejar sorte. Só corra devagar e eu ficarei feliz.
message.de_DE: Du musst mir kein Glück wünschen. Lauf einfach langsam, das reicht mir schon.
message.zh_CN: 不用祝我好运，你打慢点我就高兴了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
応援してくれなくても大丈夫だよ。
ゆっくり攻略してくれれば
私はハッピーだから。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 내 운은 안 빌어줘도 돼. 그 대신 네가 천천히 하면 될 것 같아.<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 不用祝我好運，你打慢點我就高興了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: I won't give you that luxury.
message.pt_BR: Não vou lhe dar esse luxo.
message.de_DE: Den Gefallen werde ich dir nicht tun.
message.ja_JP:
そんなワガママは
させませんよ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
